long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
JupyterLab 汉化插件，一站式 AI 开发平台 ModelArts 专用工具集。默认的JupyterLab的操作界面是英文的，通过使用插件，能够将英文的操作界面翻译成中文，方便不熟悉英语的人也能快速入手JupyterLab。
Jupyterlab Chinese plug-in, one-stop AI development platform modelarts special tool set. The default operation interface of jupyterlab is English. By using plug-ins, the English operation interface can be translated into Chinese, which is convenient for people who are not familiar with English to start jupyterlab quickly.
